Privacy Policy for Cross Stitch Chart
This is the privacy policy for Cross Stitch Chart, this policy exists to inform you about the information we receive and how we use that information.
Overview
Cross Stitch Chart does not log or store any information about how you use the app.
We will not sell your personal data to third parties.
We use anonymous information about your device and application performance to improve Cross Stitch Chart.
Acceptance of these terms
By using Cross Stitch Chart you accept the contents of this document
Changes
We reserve the right to make changes to this privacy policy. Any changes will be communicated on this page. You are advised to check for our most recent privacy policy regularly.
This document was last updated on March 6, 2022
Contact
